      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose $I_n =  \\int_{t=0}^{\\pi/2} \\cos(2nt)\\ln(\\sin t)\\,d t$ ($n\\in\\N^*$).\nCalculer $2nI_n - (2n+2)I_{n+1}$ et en déduire $I_n$ en fonction de~$n$.",
        "html": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n =  \\int_{t=0}^{\\pi/2} \\cos(2nt)\\ln(\\sin t)\\,d t\\)</span> (<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\in\\N^*\\)</span>). Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2nI_n - (2n+2)I_{n+1}\\)</span> et en déduire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "661775f9-6204-490c-b5dd-c138d97b7aff",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$2nI_n - (2n+2)I_{n+1}=0  \\Rightarrow  I_n = -\\frac\\pi{4n}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(2nI_n - (2n+2)I_{n+1}=0  \\Rightarrow  I_n = -\\frac\\pi{4n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
